INFO:

This is a Malayalam-English English-Malayalam dictionary with 85000 English words. It is highly on demand here and in many gulf countries . Students as well as businessmen are equally benefited by this software. Along with mobile phones the software runs on tablets, playbooks, notebooks etc. The software works on android, iphone , symbian, windows, blackberry and all major Java supporting platforms like samsung bada, nokia s40 etc.
Mobile Dictionary Software is a sophisticated tool for cell phones which helps to reduce the hardships in finding out Malayalam meaning of English words and vice versa.
